            "content": {
                "raw": "This needs a description and an issue.\n\nAdditionally, the \"energy\" issue in Enzo is getting really unpleasant, but because we want them to all have the same name, I think it is necessary for now.\n\nThis would be much easier solved if Enzo did the right thing or if there was a way to validate parameters in yt before fields are added.  The latter check would be surprisingly easy, but I guess as long as bandaids are the name of the game, I have no grounds to object here.",
                "html": "<p>This needs a description and an issue.</p>\n<p>Additionally, the \"energy\" issue in Enzo is getting really unpleasant, but because we want them to all have the same name, I think it is necessary for now.</p>\n<p>This would be much easier solved if Enzo did the right thing or if there was a way to validate parameters in yt before fields are added.  The latter check would be surprisingly easy, but I guess as long as bandaids are the name of the game, I have no grounds to object here.</p>",
